titles.title: A resolution honoring Gonzaga University on its 125th anniversary.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Unanimous Consent.

bill.summary: 1/31/2013--Passed Senate without amendment. Honors Gonzaga University, located in Spokane Washington, on its 125th anniversary. Applauds Gonzaga University for its commitment to its students and for instilling in them the importance of service to others and civic engagement. Congratulates its students, staff, faculty, alumni, and supporters for their many contributions in the United States and abroad.
